                            h6 About Teri
                            p Teri is a coding enthusiast who is looking for opportunities to flourish under the tutalage of experienced coders.  Please contact her if you are looking for interns or jr. web developers to mold into super coders.
                        .col-sm-4
                            h6 navigation
                            ul.unstyled
                                li
                                    a(href='/') Home
                                li
